---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about MiMaji Foundation's mission to provide clean, safe water access to communities across East Africa. Founded in 2025, we combine technology and community partnerships."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">Our Story</div>
    <h1>About <em>MiMaji Foundation</em></h1>
    <p>Clean water is a right, not a privilege. We work to make that real for every household in East Africa.</p>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C360,100 720,20 1080,60 C1260,80 1380,50 1440,60 L1440,100 L0,100Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Our Origin</div>
      <div class="section-title">Born from a Real Problem</div>
      <div class="origin-image fade-in">
        <img
          src="/nairobi-home-family-4-washing-dishes-by-the-sink-urban-homes.png"
          alt="A Nairobi family washing dishes at home, illustrating the everyday water challenges MiMaji Foundation works to solve in Kenya"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1200"
          height="600"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text fade-in">
        <p>While building <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji</a> as a water delivery platform in Nairobi, we found that the communities that needed clean water most were paying the highest prices for the worst quality. Residents in Kibera pay up to ten times more per litre than households in Karen.</p>
        <p>MiMaji Foundation was established in 2025 to close this gap: water quality testing, community education, and the <a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a> data platform that brings transparency to every household.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="bg-sand">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">What Guides Us</div>
      <div class="section-title">Our Values</div>
      <div class="about-values fade-in">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">▲</div>
          <h4>Impact First</h4>
          <p>Every decision is measured by people who gain access to clean water.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">●</div>
          <h4>Community Partnership</h4>
          <p>We co-create with the communities we serve, never impose.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">◆</div>
          <h4>Data-Driven</h4>
          <p>Real research, real testing, real numbers. No vanity metrics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">■</div>
          <h4>Sustainability</h4>
          <p>Solutions designed to be owned and maintained by communities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MiMaji Ecosystem -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">The MiMaji Ecosystem</div>
      <div class="section-title">Foundation + Platform</div>
      <div class="ecosystem-image fade-in">
        <img
          src="/Kinds-of-water-delivery-in-Nairobi-including-link-to-MiMaji.png"
          alt="The Nairobi water delivery ecosystem: boda boda riders, NCWSC tankers, handcart vendors, the MiMaji mobile app, and verified MiMaji delivery riders"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1200"
          height="500"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="ecosystem-grid fade-in">
        <div class="eco-card">
          <div class="eco-badge">Platform</div>
          <h3><a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji.co.ke</a></h3>
          <p>Kenya's water delivery technology platform connecting customers to verified, quality water suppliers.</p>
          <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-dark" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Visit Platform &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card">
          <div class="eco-badge foundation">Foundation</div>
          <h3>MiMaji Foundation</h3>
          <p>The social impact arm: testing, education, advocacy, and the MajiMap data platform.</p>
          <a href="/programs/" class="btn btn-outline-dark" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Our Programs &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Our Journey</div>
      <div class="section-title">Milestones & Roadmap</div>
      <div class="timeline fade-in">
        <div class="timeline-item completed">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
            <h4>MiMaji Platform Launch</h4>
            <p><a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji.co.ke</a> launched as Kenya's water delivery technology platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item completed">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2025</div>
            <h4>Foundation Established</h4>
            <p>MiMaji Foundation set up as the social impact arm. Nairobi Water Price Map research completed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item active">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>
            <h4>Phase 1 Active</h4>
            <p>Building <a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a>, water testing protocols, and the <a href="/water-in-schools/">schools programme</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2027</div>
            <h4>Regional Expansion</h4>
            <p>Scaling proven programmes across East Africa.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-title">Join Us in Our Mission</div>
    <p>Partner, volunteer, or support our work. There's a place for you at MiMaji Foundation.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/take-action/" class="btn btn-white">Take Action &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/programs/" class="btn btn-outline">View Programs</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .origin-image,
  .ecosystem-image {
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.12);
  }

  .origin-image img,
  .ecosystem-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .ecosystem-image {
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .about-text a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.08);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .value-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ecosystem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .eco-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .eco-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.1);
  }

  .eco-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--blue-light);
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .eco-badge.foundation {
    background: rgba(26, 158, 143, 0.1);
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .eco-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .eco-card h3 a {
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .eco-card h3 a:hover {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .eco-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ecosystem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-values {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-values {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 7px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 0.3rem;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 3px solid var(--white);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-item.completed .timeline-marker {
    background: var(--teal);
  }

  .timeline-item.active .timeline-marker {
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(244, 169, 48, 0.2);
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .timeline-content a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
